# Group Cities
Cities can be accessed here.
Cities must be part of a Province. 


Editable Attributes

+ None 


## Cities Collection [/cities?include=includes&limit=limit]
+ Parameters
    + limit (optional, number, `1`) ... Numerical `limit` to apply to how many records are returned.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `province`, or `all`

