## City [/cities/id?include=includes]
Get a single City object 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the City to perform action with. Has example value.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `province`, or `all`

